#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:12
msgid "Undo"
msgstr "元に戻す"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:12
msgid "Redo"
msgstr "やり直す"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:12
msgid "History"
msgstr "履歴"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:17
msgid "Undo History"
msgstr "編集履歴"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:19
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:22
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Undo History"
msgid "Undo History Docker"
msgstr "編集履歴"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:25
msgid ".. image:: /images/dockers/Krita_Undo_History_Docker.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:26
msgid ""
"This docker allows you to quickly shift between undo states, and even go "
"back in time far more quickly than rapidly reusing the :kbd:`Ctrl + Z` "
"shortcut."
msgstr ""
"このドッキングパネルで元に戻した状態と素早く行き来することができ、:kbd:`Ctrl "
"+ Z` ショートカットを連打するよりはるかに素早く時間をさかのぼることもできま"
"す。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:28
msgid "Cumulate Undo"
msgstr "累積で元に戻す"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:31
msgid "Cumulative Undo"
msgstr "累積で元に戻す"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:33
msgid ""
"Cumulative Undo is a feature of Krita that allows merging similar undo "
"states basing on their time separation. It makes the undo history cleaner."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:42
msgid ""
"Cumulative Undo settings are located under :guilabel:`General` "
"-> :guilabel:`Miscellaneous` page of Krita settings dialog"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:45
msgid ".. image:: /images/dockers/Cumulative_Undo_General_Settings.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:46
msgid ""
"In the advanced section of the settings you can configure the following "
"properties:"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:49
msgid ".. image:: /images/dockers/Cumulative_Undo_Advanced_Settings.png"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:50
msgid "Wait before merging strokes"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:51
msgid ""
"The minimal age (in seconds) of the strokes to become subject to merging. "
"This option allows you to keep undo for last N seconds intact."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:52
msgid "Exclude last strokes from merge"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:53
msgid ""
"The minimal number of strokes that undo history should have before merging "
"will start. This option allows you to keep N last strokes intact."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:54
msgid "Max interval group strokes"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:55
msgid ""
"The maximum break the user takes between doing two strokes that can be "
"considered to belong the same group. The lower the value, the more "
"irrelevant strokes will be merged."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:57
msgid "Max group duration"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:57
msgid ""
"The maximum duration of a single group. When a group becomes too long, Krita "
"just starts a new one."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:59
msgid ""
"Apart from these options, Krita will make sure that strokes of different "
"colors, brush presets or blending modes are not merged together."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/dockers/undo_history.rst:-1
msgid "Overview of the undo history docker."
msgstr "編集履歴ドッキングパネルの概要。"

#~ msgid "Split strokes."
#~ msgstr "描線を分離"

#~ msgid "Start merging time"
#~ msgstr "統合時間の開始"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The amount of seconds required to consider a group of strokes to be worth "
#~ "one undo step."
#~ msgstr "元に戻す1ステップに相当するストロークの秒数です。"

#~ msgid "Group time"
#~ msgstr "グループ化の時間"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "According to this parameter -- groups are made. Every stroke is put into "
#~ "the same group until two consecutive strokes have a time gap of more than "
#~ "T seconds. Then a new group is started."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "この引数で -- グループが作られます。この設定された秒数以上の間隔が空くまで"
#~ "すべてのストロークが同じグループに入れられます。経過した後に新しいグループ"
#~ "が始まります。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "A user may want to keep the ability of Undoing/Redoing his/her last N "
#~ "strokes. Once N is crossed -- the earlier strokes are merged into the "
#~ "group's first stroke."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "特定の数の一番新しいストロークを元に戻す/やり直す機能は残しておきたいユー"
#~ "ザもいるでしょう。指定の数を経過したら -- それ以前のストロークはグループの"
#~ "最初のストロークに統合されます。"
